sentences.english: In the case of local purchases of equipment and supplies, governments shall provide assurance of tax-free procurement.
sentences.chinese: 如果在当地采购设备和供应品，政府应保证免税采购。

sentences.english: More medical and surgical supplies are in the pipeline.
sentences.chinese: 正在运送更多的医疗和手术供应品。

sentences.english: I’m convinced that the provincial government will provide provisional provisions.
sentences.chinese: 我深信地方政府将提供临时供应品。

sentences.english: The supply ship refreshed the submarines between battles.
sentences.chinese: 补给船利用战斗间隙给潜水艇以新的供应品。

sentences.english: Horses bore supplies up the steep mountain.
sentences.chinese: 马匹驮着供应品走上陡峭的山路。

sentences.english: Sea voyages last long and it is necessary to take large supplies of provision.
sentences.chinese: 海上航行持续时间长，这就有必要带着大批供应品。

sentences.english: Buyer shall keep a logbook of operation for the Supplies.
sentences.chinese: 买方应记录供应品的运行日志。
